@node "History" "Program History"
    Version @{b}1.00@{ub}  (5/1/1995)

      - First public release.


    Version @{b}1.01@{ub}  (6/1/1995)

      - Bugfixes
        + File locks & memory not cleared if there was a file read error
          or suitable CLASS entry could not be found.
        + Wrong error message reported under certain circumstances.


    Version @{b}1.02@{ub}  (7/1/1995)

      - Features added
        + Added @{"APPNAME" link "ConfigToolTypes" 0} tooltype
        + Added @{"CONFIG" link "ConfigToolTypes" 0} control entry, allowing you to select which config
          file to load and use for each copy of IDer running.


    Version @{b}1.03@{ub}  (7/1/1995)

      - Bugfixes
        + Corrected error if IDer tried to load more than file, via any
          method, in one session.  Bug was introduced in 1.01
        + Cleaned up AppIcon message handling


    Version @{b}1.04@{ub}  (8/1/1995)

      - Bugfixes
        + Corrected error with APPNAME entry.  Now displays correct text.
        + Fixed minor errors with final commandline layout.
        + Changed gadgets on AppIcon @{"`About'" link "UsageWorkbench" 0} requester.
        + Corrected documentation in several places.


    Version @{b}1.05@{ub}  (15/1/1995)

      - No idea what changes made


    Version @{b}1.06@{ub}  (18/2/1997)

      - Released to the public domain.  Ignore all mentions of Shareware
        and the like.  Source code is included in the archive if anyone
        wants to continue development.

@endnode
